window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Great God spots trouble on the horizon.</b></p> <p>Demons scheme in the shadows. A myth golem wreaks havoc across the continent. Trouble is brewing in the Yixine empire.</p> <p>All of these cataclysms are eclipsed by an apocalypse greater than them all—Neave's arrival at the capital.</p> <p>Torn between rehabilitating the profoundly sick cultivator society and wiping the slate clean, Neave gathers power on his journey to find the right solution. He grows suspicious of even his own thoughts, however, and it soon becomes clear that it won't be easy.</p> <p>But all of that is secondary to solving the immediate problem on his hands—not dying from all the abuse his body has gone through.</p>"; 
